messageBody:
Welcome to the JUnit community, but please understand that it will
help your question asking if you take some time to read this classic
document first:

http://www.catb.org/~esr/faqs/smart-questions.html

Then head over to http://junit.org/ where you willl find the junit
java library. Please consider using the Google search engine for other
product information that you find you need.

Simon
